data.description: Enchanting Oceanview Condo located in the exclusive and sought-after The Dawn Condominiums. Voted Best Condo in Galveston! This Gorgeous 1bed/1full bath Condo offers tile throughout, high ceilings, stone countertops in Kitchen & Bath, Stainless Steel Appliances, new paint 2021, new AC 2020 & new roof 2023. Conveys furnished with Exclusions. The Refrigerator, Washer & Dryer stay! The Naked Mermaid has been a popular vacation rental on Airbnb due to its location, gorgeous finishes & amazing balcony views. The Dawn is pet-friendly & features 2 magnificent pools, Hot tub, Fitness Center, Clubhouse, bbq area & beautifully landscaped grounds for those evening strolls. The Condo is on the 3rd floor in building 11 which gives you panoramic views of the Gulf and Babes Beach. Relax on your large balcony as you take in the endless scenic sunset views with your favorite drink while listening to the seagulls and the amazing ocean waves. This condo will not last!!! Call for an appointment Today!
